oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.flex.runtime
Enum FlexfieldTranslations

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<FlexfieldTranslations>
      oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.flex.runtime.FlexfieldTranslations
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FlexfieldTranslations>
public enum FlexfieldTranslations
extends java.lang.Enum<FlexfieldTranslations>

ApplCore Internal Use Only. Applications should not use this class.

This class defines groups of translatable resources for a flexfield and a mechanism to access the resources at runtime.
